---
---

<section id="about" class="relative py-24 md:py-40 overflow-hidden">
	<div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.02] dark:opacity-[0.015]"
		style="background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 1px 1px, currentColor 1px, transparent 0); background-size: 32px 32px;">
	</div>

	<div class="max-w-[1400px] mx-auto px-4 md:px-8 lg:px-12">
		<div class="reveal mb-16 md:mb-24">
			<p class="text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.5em] text-amber-600/50 dark:text-amber-400/40 mb-4">The Artist</p>
			<h2 class="text-4xl md:text-7xl font-bold">About</h2>
			<div class="h-[1px] bg-[#1a1a1a]/5 dark:bg-white/5 mt-8 line-draw"></div>
		</div>

		<div class="grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-8 md:gap-6 lg:gap-8 items-start">
			<div class="md:col-span-5 relative reveal">
				<div class="relative">
					<div class="aspect-[3/4] rounded-xl md:rounded-2xl overflow-hidden img-reveal">
						<img src="/artworks/varsha.jpg" alt="Varsha — The Artist" class="w-full h-full object-cover" loading="lazy" />
					</div>
					<div class="absolute -top-3 -left-3 md:-top-4 md:-left-4 w-16 h-16 md:w-20 md:h-20 border-l border-t border-amber-500/20 dark:border-amber-400/15 rounded-tl-xl"></div>
					<div class="absolute -bottom-3 -right-3 md:-bottom-4 md:-right-4 w-16 h-16 md:w-20 md:h-20 border-r border-b border-amber-500/20 dark:border-amber-400/15 rounded-br-xl"></div>
				</div>
				<div class="absolute -bottom-6 -right-2 md:-bottom-8 md:-right-6 bg-[#faf9f6] dark:bg-[#0a0a0a] border border-amber-500/15 dark:border-amber-400/10 rounded-xl md:rounded-2xl px-5 py-4 md:px-7 md:py-5">
					<span class="block text-2xl md:text-3xl font-['Playfair_Display',serif] font-bold text-amber-600/80 dark:text-amber-400/70">3+</span>
					<span class="text-[9px] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-amber-600/40 dark:text-amber-400/30">Years of Art</span>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="md:col-span-7 md:pl-8 lg:pl-16">
				<div class="reveal reveal-delay-1">
					<h3 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-2 leading-tight">Varsha</h3>
					<p class="text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-[#1a1a1a]/25 dark:text-white/20 mb-8 md:mb-10 font-['Space_Mono',monospace]">Sketch Artist & Visual Storyteller</p>
				</div>

				<div class="space-y-5 text-[#1a1a1a]/45 dark:text-white/35 text-sm md:text-[15px] leading-[1.8] reveal reveal-delay-2">
					<p>Every sketch begins with a feeling. Working primarily in graphite and charcoal, I'm drawn to the way simple pencil strokes can capture emotion, light, and the quiet beauty in everyday moments.</p>
					<p>My journey started with a love for observation — noticing the way shadows fall across a face, how textures shift in natural light. Each piece is a conversation between the paper and me.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="mt-12 md:mt-16 reveal reveal-delay-3">
					<p class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-[#1a1a1a]/20 dark:text-white/20 mb-6">My Process</p>
					<div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 md:gap-6">
						{[
							{ num: '01', title: 'Observe', desc: 'Study the subject, find the story' },
							{ num: '02', title: 'Sketch', desc: 'Rough composition and values' },
							{ num: '03', title: 'Refine', desc: 'Detail, texture, and emotion' },
						].map(step => (
							<div class="group">
								<span class="text-[10px] font-['Space_Mono',monospace] text-[#1a1a1a]/15 dark:text-white/15 group-hover:text-amber-500/40 dark:group-hover:text-amber-400/30 transition-colors">{step.num}</span>
								<p class="text-sm md:text-base font-['Playfair_Display',serif] mt-2 mb-1">{step.title}</p>
								<p class="text-[11px] text-[#1a1a1a]/25 dark:text-white/25 leading-relaxed">{step.desc}</p>
							</div>
						))}
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-6 md:gap-8 mt-12 md:mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-[#1a1a1a]/5 dark:border-white/5 reveal reveal-delay-4">
					{[
						{ num: '50+', label: 'Artworks' },
						{ num: '20+', label: 'Commissions' },
						{ num: '100+', label: 'Followers' },
					].map(stat => (
						<div>
							<span class="block text-2xl md:text-4xl font-['Playfair_Display',serif] font-bold">{stat.num}</span>
							<span class="text-[9px] md:text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-[#1a1a1a]/20 dark:text-white/20 mt-1">{stat.label}</span>
						</div>
					))}
				</div>

				<div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 md:gap-4 mt-10 md:mt-12 reveal reveal-delay-4">
					<a href="https://www.instagram.com/sketching_.wid_.heart" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
						class="magnetic-btn px-7 md:px-9 py-3.5 md:py-4 bg-amber-500 dark:bg-amber-400 text-white dark:text-[#0a0a0a] text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] font-medium hover:bg-amber-600 dark:hover:bg-amber-300 transition-all rounded-full text-center">
						Follow on Instagram
					</a>
					<a href="https://www.instagram.com/varsha.r_.o" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
						class="magnetic-btn px-7 md:px-9 py-3.5 md:py-4 border border-[#1a1a1a]/10 dark:border-white/10 text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-[#1a1a1a]/50 dark:text-white/50 hover:text-[#1a1a1a] dark:hover:text-white hover:border-[#1a1a1a]/25 dark:hover:border-white/25 transition-all rounded-full text-center">
						Personal IG
					</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
